{"tid":2144204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話葉舒華 肥舒 減左肥話？？","createTime":"2020-08-07T14:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:23:18.000Z","uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ee5de02c36340494a35dc4b4b773ccd7b1c1c3","tid":2144204,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"本來隻腳已經唔長點解要放任自己變成咁肥 <br />\n可能係普通人身上係微胖嘅QQ女仔但係佢係一個偶像<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經冇實力唔跳得唔唱得 而家連身材管理都搞成咁<br />\n佢同美延企埋一齊真係搞到唔知邊個先係門面<br />\n明明自己個底好好但係唔識得管理之前佢哋接咗個涼鞋廣告佢嘅鏡頭好似幾乎都冇。直到今次回歸佢存在感都係勁低（唔好同我講MV多鏡頭）佢嘅定位係門面但係呢個門面完全冇門面嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39j55FM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39j55FM.png&h=75eabd94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdbTu7G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdbTu7G.png&h=81a280ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16ea63ae0047b7cb8707d86be410fa4460a770a5","tid":2144204,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"佢mv pink pink shirt波仔肉係幾吸引"},{"pid":"c80f604a8e8e732692013e0d9bb129645cf32440","tid":2144204,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfc535246e941d414e3126317e788f06218c8f3","tid":2144204,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"16ea63ae0047b7cb8707d86be410fa4460a770a5","tid":2144204,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"佢mv pink pink shirt波仔肉係幾吸引"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T